  "title": "Chartering & Commercial Operations Executive",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a Senior Commercial Executive for one of our shipowner clients. The role involves chartering execution across spot, COA, and time charters, commercial documentation, and acting as a key interface with charterers, brokers, and vessel managers. The role also supports fleet deployment planning, market analysis, and business development initiatives. The ideal candidate should have at least 3–5 years’ experience in chartering, commercial, or shipping operations, strong commercial judgment, and the ambition to progress into a future Commercial Manager role. </p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u><strong> </strong></p><ul><li>Manage and execute chartering activities across spot, COA, and time charter fixtures</li><li>Prepare, negotiate, and administer charter party agreements and related documentation</li><li>Serve as the primary commercial point of contact for assigned vessels, charterers, and brokers</li><li>Monitor vessel utilisation, hire performance, off-hire events, and key commercial KPIs</li><li>Produce commercial performance reports, fleet deployment outlooks, and market analysis</li><li>Support business development through commercial proposals, market assessments, and deal evaluation</li><li>Provide commercial input into fleet deployment decisions, new projects, and operational planning</li><li>Support customer and partner relationships, freight benchmarking, and competitor\nmonitoring</li></ul><p><u><strong>Qualifications:</strong></u><strong> </strong></p><ul><li>3–5 years’ experience in chartering, commercial, or shipping operations</li><li>Tanker experience preferred; exposure to crude oil or liquefied gas tankers is a\nstrong advantage</li><li>Solid understanding of charter parties with strong commercial judgment</li><li>Strong analytical capability with effective communication and stakeholder management skills</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, please send your application to <a href=\"mailto:talentagent@innergy-consulting.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">talentagent@innergy-consulting.com</a> <br />\nWe regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Thank you for your\nunderstanding.</p>",
